snippet.title: Dave the Diver - Ichiban's Holiday DLC Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Ichiban ventures into the Blue Hole, in hopes for a much-needed getaway.

But he’s in for more than just a holiday— unsettled threats and new, unforgettable friendships lie ahead!

Get ready to join Ichiban and the Blue Hole crew for a wild ride in DAVE THE DIVER: Ichiban's Holiday DLC, arriving in April.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #davethediver
